snippet.title: CNC EA Gameplay Trailer #2 - Cattle and Crops - Farming Simulation 🚜🐂🌾
snippet.description:
Support the development and register for Early Access: https://www.cattleandcrops.com/kickstarter
------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

We're very proud to present our second official ingame early-access gameplay trailer. 

Machines: 
0:10 - Claas Axion 940 + Hammer CornKing Maize
0:30 - Claas Axion 940 + Deutz 7250 + Hawe SLW50 + Claas Jaguar 970 + Orbis 900
1:00 - Deutz 7250 +  Köckerling Rebell 410
1:25 - Claas Arion 540 + Stapel VT18000
1:30 - Claas Axion 940 + Lemken Juwel 6+1
1:40 - Claas Arion 540 + Joskin Betimax 9000
1:45 - Claas Arion 540 + FL100 + Bressel und Lade SL + Mercedes Benz MB Trac 1400 + Strautmann Verti-Mix 1801 Double 
2:05 - Mercedes Benz MB Trac 1000 + Strautmann Verti-Mix 1801 Double 
2:12 - Claas Tucano 570 + Claas Vario 970 + Claas Trailer 521
2:25 - Claas Axion 940 + Claas Tucano 570 + Claas Vario 970 + Claas Trailer 521 + Joskin Delta-Cap 5025/12DR100
2:55 - Claas Axion 940 and some Bulls :)

We are excited to hear your feedback. Have fun!

Stay in touch:
